     * <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Least_squares">Wikipedia</a>,
     * or
     * <a href="http://mathworld.wolfram.com/LeastSquaresFitting.html">MathWorld</a>,
     * equations (34) and (35) for a particular case.
